{"tid":2005855,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科學家在英國淡水蝦體內發現古柯鹼","createTime":"2020-05-07T11:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T13:48:16.000Z","uid":343294,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"caee68ff70b283b47411a35ed74c79fed69bd42f","tid":2005855,"uid":343294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:26:29.000Z","msg":"科學家在英國淡水蝦體內發現古柯鹼<br />\n<br />\n2019年 5月 2日<br />\n<br />\nl研究人員收集英國薩福克郡的河流淡水蝦<br />\n研究發現，科學家在測試河流中的化學品時，在淡水蝦體內發現古柯鹼（又稱可卡因）。<br />\n英國倫敦大學國王學院的研究人員與薩福克大學（University of Suffolk）合作，在薩福克郡的15個不同地點進行測試。<br />\n報告中提到，在所有淡水蝦的樣本中都發現古柯鹼。<br />\n<br />\n其它違禁毒品，例如氯胺酮（俗稱K仔），都在大部份淡水蝦樣本中找到。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員稱這個是一個「令人意外」的發現。<br />\n<br />\n走私逾千海龜大案揭示全球第四大非法貿易<br />\n<br />\n下水道裏是否充滿了違禁毒品？<br />\n<br />\n薩福克大學教授尼克&middot;貝利（Prof. Nic Bury）稱，「如果要判斷在海洋生物中找到古柯鹼，是一個薩福克郡、整個英國或是世界的共同問題，我們需要作更多研究。」<br />\n<br />\n「環境健康議題引起公眾關注，原因是問題涉及氣候變化及微塑膠污染。」<br />\n<br />\n「不過，英國『隱性』化學品污染（例如毒品）對野生動物健康的影響，需要得到更多的關注。」<br />\n<br />\n薩福克大學教授尼克&middot;貝利是其中一名研究人員。<br />\n<br />\n發表在科學期刊《國際環境》上的報告研究了各種野生動物，例如淡水蝦，受各種微污染物影響的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n除了毒品外，在收取的淡水蝦樣本中，也發現其他違禁農藥及違禁藥。不過，他們表示，它們對生物的潛在影響「應該較低」。<br />\n<br />\n科學家在英國薩福克郡15個不同地點收取樣本<br />\n<br />\n英國倫敦大學國王學院利安&middot;巴朗博士（Dr. Leon Barron）表示，「在野生動物中經常發現毒品的情況令人感到意外」。<br />\n<br />\n「我們可能期望在倫敦這樣的城市地區看到這些，但不會在較小的地方或鄉村地區看到這些。在淡水蝦中發現很久以前已被禁止使用的農藥，為我們帶來艱巨的挑戰，因為我們不清楚它們的來源。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-48130298?ocid=socialflow_facebook&amp;at_custom3=BBC+Chinese+(Traditional)&amp;at_medium=custom7&amp;at_custom4=BB241B42-9028-11EA-B831-5FFB923C408C&amp;at_custom2=facebook_page&amp;at_custom1=%5Bpost+type%5D&amp;at_campaign=64\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-48130298%3Focid%3Dsocialflow_facebook%26at_custom3%3DBBC%2BChinese%2B%28Traditional%29%26at_medium%3Dcustom7%26at_custom4%3DBB241B42-9028-11EA-B831-5FFB923C408C%26at_custom2%3Dfacebook_page%26at_custom1%3D%255Bpost%2Btype%255D%26at_campaign%3D64&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdY2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=49e18def\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-48130298%3Focid%3Dsocialflow_facebook%26at_custom3%3DBBC%2BChinese%2B%28Traditional%29%26at_medium%3Dcustom7%26at_custom4%3DBB241B42-9028-11EA-B831-5FFB923C408C%26at_custom2%3Dfacebook_page%26at_custom1%3D%255Bpost%2Btype%255D%26at_campaign%3D64&h=54613e32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-48130298?ocid=socialflow_facebook&amp;at_custom3=BBC+Chinese+(Traditional)&amp;at_medium=custom7&amp;at_custom4=BB241B42-9028-11EA-B831-5FFB923C408C&amp;at_custom2=facebook_page&amp;at_custom1=%5Bpost+type%5D&amp;at_campaign=64</a>"},{"pid":"fd742c228bebe636d9d6ffcb8814fa3df3e919cb","tid":2005855,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:37:55.000Z","msg":"英國研究信唔信好？"},{"pid":"ae3b631abff26222cf6c125833386aeb616f208b","tid":2005855,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:38:56.000Z","msg":"捉蝦食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7eff426063bbd1c3c4192d95fc44d375bd2a13","tid":2005855,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:39:21.000Z","msg":"get high every day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c5efa18b1c5dd45ade9ca38cef30d4dcba43ab","tid":2005855,"uid":340004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"烤爹U<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc53b07a88bae934752e145a874fde7c1c391ae","tid":2005855,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"吸蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ca9134dc3ed4c80209a83819f1ffa781ec233f","tid"